node_7.description: This is Isabella Rodriguez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, go to Hobbs Cafe and open it at 8:00 am, go over the day's menu and prepare the ingredients needed by 9:00 am, start serving customers at 10:00 am, take a break for lunch at 12:00 pm, continue serving customers until 8:00 pm, close Hobbs Cafe and clean up by 9:00 pm, go back home, watch a little bit of TV and have dinner at 8:30 pm.
